(0) READ-ITEM ARR N
(1) COMPARE ARR(I) WITH ARR(I-1)
    IF GREATER OR EQUAL GO TO OPERATION 3
    IF LESS GO TO OPERATION 2
(2) TRANSFER ARR(I) TO TEMP
    TRANSFER ARR(I-1) TO ARR(I)
    TRANSFER TEMP TO ARR(I-1)
    DECREASE I BY 1
    GO TO OPERATION 1
(3) INCREASE I BY 1
    IF I LESS THAN N GO TO OPERATION 1
(4) STOP
